 2019-07132019-06-02,  CH,  ,  , 
ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of MANDY WOODLAND of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Douglas Feasby, whose term has expired.
